{
  "texts": [
    "Aygun et al.",
    "67 similarly generated synthetic proofs with hindsight experience replay 68, providing a smooth range of theorem difficulty to aid learning similar to our work.",
    "AlphaGeometry, however, is not trained on existing conjectures curated by humans and does not learn from proof attempts on the target theorems.",
    "Their approach is thus orthogonal and can be used to further improve AlphaGeometry.",
    "Most similar to our work is Firoiu et al."
  ]
}